data.title: Princess Louise of Sweden Norway, Queen Denmark (1851
meta_keywords: Autographed Cabinet Card of Princess Louise of Sweden and Norway

Queen of Denmark (1851-1926). 
Daughter of Charles XV of Sweden and and Louise of Oranje - Nassau Princess of the Netherlands. She married Frederick VIII and became Queen of Denmark.
